uk.gov.gchq.palisade.audit.service.request

Class AuditRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.service.request.Request
      • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.audit.service.request.AuditRequest

  • public class AuditRequest
extends Request
    This is the object that is passed to the AuditService to be able to store an audit record. The default information is what resources was being accessed, who is accessing the resource, why are they accessing it and what filters/transformations are being applied to the data. An optional extra is to add an exception to be able to log errors that might occur so the audit log reflects that actually the user did not get access to the data, and why that was.
